"title": "8206: Christlikeness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8206: christlikeness",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The process by which believers are conformed to the likeness of Jesus Christ, especially in relation to obedience to and trust in God. Through the Holy Spirit, God refashions believers in the image of his Son, who is set before them as a model of the form of the redeemed life.</p>\n<h2>Believers are to become Christlike</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5\">PHP 2:5</a></strong> <em>Paul is arguing that believers must allow God to make them Christlike, which is the natural goal of their process of growing in faith. Christlikeness is not achieved by people merely trying to imitate Jesus Christ, but by God making believers more like his Son in sanctification, through the Spirit.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:15\">JHN 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:13\">EPH 4:11–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8-Phil3:11\">PHP 3:8–3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20-Phil3:21\">PHP 3:20–3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:6\">1JN 2:6</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit makes believers Christlike</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:9\">ROM 8:5–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Christlikeness is the aim of discipleship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:25\">MAT 10:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:40\">LUK 6:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:6\">1JN 2:6</a></p>\n<h2>Christlikeness is based on total commitment to Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:57-Luke9:62\">LUK 9:57–9:62</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9\">MAT 9:9</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14\">MRK 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27\">LUK 5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22\">LUK 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:43\">JHN 1:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27\">JHN 10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:9\">2JN 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>The demonstration of Christlikeness</h2>\n<h3>In costly sacrifice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34-Mark8:35\">MRK 8:34–8:35</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23-Luke9:24\">LUK 9:23–9:24</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21-1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:21–2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:38\">MAT 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26-Luke14:27\">LUK 14:26–14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:19\">JHN 21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:1\">1PE 4:1</a></p>\n<h3>In humility and service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:26-Matt20:28\">MAT 20:26–20:28</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:43-Mark10:45\">MRK 10:43–10:45</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:29\">MAT 11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:35\">MRK 9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:24-Luke22:26\">LUK 22:24–22:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:14-John13:15\">JHN 13:14–13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:4-Phil2:5\">PHP 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>In love for other believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12\">JHN 15:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:34\">JHN 13:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:17\">JHN 15:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:2\">EPH 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25\">EPH 5:25</a></p>\n<h3>In a readiness to forgive others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:12\">MAT 6:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:4\">LUK 11:4</a></p>\n<h3>In sharing Jesus Christ's mission to the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:19\">MAT 4:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:17\">MRK 1:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:21\">JHN 20:21</a></p>\n<h3>By following godly examples that imitate Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:1\">EPH 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5-1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:5–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">1TH 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:12\">HEB 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:7-Heb13:8\">HEB 13:7–13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:11\">3JN 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Christlikeness is part of God's re-creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:27\">GEN 1:26–1:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:24\">EPH 4:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:10\">COL 3:10</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The process of becoming Christlike</h2>\n<h3>It is the purpose for which believers are saved</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28-Rom8:29\">ROM 8:28–8:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:10\">EPH 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>It continues in the experience of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a></strong></p>\n<h3>It will be complete when believers finally share Jesus Christ's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2-1John3:3\">1JN 3:2–3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:15\">PSA 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49-1Cor15:53\">1CO 15:49–15:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:19\">GAL 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20-Phil3:21\">PHP 3:20–3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:4\">COL 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:17\">1JN 4:17</a></p>",
